DESCRIPTION

DenSoft ist a light-weight php web application framework that
provides the following features:

- a request routing mechanism
- MVC building blocks
- the Repository pattern for de-coupling business logic from data access
- simple templating and theming mechanisms
- a default class auto-loader
- a lazily-loaded database connection
- and more...

DEPENDENCIES

DenSoft runs on PHP 5.2+.
DenSoft requires o external libraries.
